---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="Canchero - Inicio">
	<section class="bg-[url('/public/bg.jpg')] bg-cover bg-no-repeat text-[#1f2433] w-full h-auto  flex items-center py-[50px] px-[300px]
                    max-lg:px-[50px] 
                    max-sm:px-[30px] 
    ">
        <div class=" bg-white/80 rounded-3xl h-full w-full z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center py-8 px-10">
            <h2 class="text-5xl mb-4 font-bold 
                    max-lg:text-4xl         
                    ">Canchero</h2>
            <p class="text-[18px] mb-[40px] px-10 
                    max-xl:px-8 max-xl:mb-[30px] 
                    max-lg:text-[16px] 
                    max-sm:text-[14px] max-sm:px-0 max-sm:mb-[15px]
                    ">Reserva desde la comodidad de tu casa las diferentes canchas sinteticas aliadas. Encuentra informacion clave a la hora de elegir tu cancha, horarios disponibles, precios por hora, ubicacion, entre mucha mas informacion la cual te ayudara a elegir el escenario que mas se acomode a tus necesidades.</p>
            <a class="flex items-center justify-center shadow hover:shadow-xl h-auto w-auto py-[8px] px-[35px] text-white hover:text-[#1f2433] bg-[#1f2433] hover:bg-white hover:border-solid border-[#1f2433] border-2 text-xl rounded-3xl font-bold 
                    max-lg:text-[18px] max-lg:py-[6px] max-lg:px-[30px]
                    max-sm:text-[16px] max-sm:py-[4px] max-sm:px-[25px]
            " href="/login">
                Ingresa ahora
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="h-auto w-full py-14 bg-white flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="mx-[100px] h-auto w-full bg-neutral-200 shadow-2xl rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center gap-10 py-12 px-12
                    max-lg:flex-col max-lg:gap-6 max-lg:mx-[50px] max-lg:px-10 max-lg:py-10
                    max-sm:mx-[20px] max-sm:px-8 max-sm:py-8 max-sm:gap-8
        ">
            <div class="h-auto w-full bg-white rounded-3xl flex flex-col  items-center justify-center text-center px-[50px]
                        max-lg:h-[300px] max-lg:ml-0 
                        max-sm:px-[20px]
            ">

                <div class="h-[100px] flex items-end">
                    <svg class="max-lg:w-[55px] max-lg:h-[55px] 
                                max-sm:w-[45px] max-sm:h-[45px] max-sm:mb-3
