                </div>

                <div class="text-[#1f2433] h-[350px] w-[full] flex flex-col justify-start pt-5
                            max-lg:h-[200px]
                ">
                    <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-8
                            max-lg:text-3xl max-lg:mb-2 max-lg:mt-2 
                            max-sm:text-2xl
                    ">Confianza</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl 
                            max-lg:text-[17px] max-lg:leading-[25px]
                            max-sm:text-[15px] max-sm:leading-[20px]
                    ">Con nuestro sistema tendras la seguridad de que nustras canchas aliadas agenden el escenario deportivo a la hora apartada.</p>
                    
                </div>

                <div class="h-[100px] flex items-start justify-center
                            max-sm:items-center
                ">
                    <a class="flex items-center justify-center font-bold shadow hover:shadow-xl h-[50px] w-[200px] text-white hover:text-[#1f2433] bg-[#1f2433] hover:bg-white hover:border-solid border-[#1f2433] border-2 text-2xl rounded-3xl
                                max-lg:h-[35px] max-lg:w-[150px] max-lg:text-xl
                    " href="/login">
                        ¡Ingresa ya!
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="h-auto w-full bg-white rounded-3xl flex flex-col  items-center justify-center text-center px-[50px]
                        max-lg:h-[300px]  max-lg:mr-0 
                        max-sm:px-[20px]
            ">

                <div class="h-[100px] flex items-end">
                    <svg class="max-lg:w-[55px] max-lg:h-[55px] 
                                max-sm:w-[45px] max-sm:h-[45px] max-sm:mb-3
